MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2006-1259. State ex rel. Coles v. Granville.

In Mandamus. On motions for contempt and for leave to file a supplement to the appendix of the motion for contempt. Motion for contempt denied. Motion for leave to file a supplement to the appendix of the motion for contempt denied as moot.

O’Donnell, J., not participating.
